Supreme Court — Appellate Term, June, 1901.

Before Scott, P. J., Beach aftd Fitzgerald, JJ.

Joseph Rosaler, Appellant, v. Frank Greenberg, Respondent. Appeal from a judgment rendered in favor of the defendant in the Municipal Court of the city of New York, fifth district, borough of Manhattan. Bernhard Ginsberg, for appellant; Abraham B. Schleimer, for respondent.

Judgment affirmed, with costs. No opinion.
